Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.56,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}大丈夫だよ　ぜったいへいき！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.11,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}とりあえず試してみよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.40,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}ムズカシイこと抜きで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.65,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}ドキドキに飛び乗ろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:15.28,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}胸のおくにずっと抱いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:20.45,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}イメージとね　勇気とが重なり合う瞬間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.00,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}飛べるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:26.08,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}めーいっぱい　高くぎゅーん！と
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.75,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}全力で上昇↑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:33.97,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}光る大空を　シュワーッて駆けめぐろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.05,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}いっせーの！ぐるぐるびゅーん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.68,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}チカラ合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.48,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}そこで回転です！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.10,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}アリで　ナシで　やっぱアリアリ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.94,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}希望・野望・鼓動　増し増し
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:53.19,IN-JP_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}描いてくコントレイル
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.55,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}從未見過的全新夢想
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.22,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}想要看看…也給你看看…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.68,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}想要前往更高的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.77,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}但是心懷不安
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.56,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}別擔心 一定沒問題！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.11,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}總之先來試一試吧！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.40,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}不要想著有多難
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.65,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}跟隨心跳起飛吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.65,0:18:15.28,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}一直珍藏在心中的願景
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.28,0:18:20.45,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}與勇氣重合交織的瞬間…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.00,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}就能翱翔天空！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.00,0:18:26.08,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}加速衝向高空
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.75,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}全力向上爬升
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.75,0:18:33.97,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}咻地一聲穿梭在閃亮天空
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.05,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}一起骨碌骨碌byun！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.68,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}彼此齊心協力
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.48,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}這裡要繞個圈！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.10,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}可以？ 不行？ 當然可以可以
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.94,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}希望 野心 心動 全都加量
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.94,0:18:53.19,IN-CH_EP01_2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HC5B0FF&\blur2}逐漸描繪出那一道尾跡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「わたしとみんなのうた」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:14.19,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ねえ　今日はどんな一日だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:17.32,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ねえねえ　一緒に話そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:21.99,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}空に光るひとつ星　星座になってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:27.70,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}もしも何かあったら　もしも何もなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:34.08,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}いつでも傍にいたい　約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:36.33,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ぎゅっと…ぐっと…じんと…きゅんと…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.34,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}手と手繋いだら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.84,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}暗い夜を　照らす朝日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:50.22,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}心と心強くなる　きらめく今
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:56.81,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}私はみんなを　もっと好きになる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:02.74,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}みんなも　私をそう思えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:06.99,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ここにいる意味を探しながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:10.49,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}笑顔だって涙だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:13.75,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}全てを歌って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:16.50,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ららら…わたしと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:19.54,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ららら…みんなと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:24.55,ED-JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ららら…わたしとみんなのうた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:14.19,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}你說  今天一天怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:17.32,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}來吧來吧  一起來聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:21.99,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}空中閃耀的第一顆星  逐漸化為星座
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:27.70,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}就算碰到什麼事  就算什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:34.08,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}我們也約好了  要一直在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:36.33,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}緊緊地…  用力地…  感動地…  心動地…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.34,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}牽起彼此的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.84,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}朝陽照亮黑暗夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:50.22,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}大家的內心更加堅強  現在閃耀光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:56.81,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}我會更加喜歡大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:02.74,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}希望大家也更喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:06.99,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}尋找著來到這裡的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:10.49,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}不論笑容還是淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:13.75,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}都一齊歌頌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:16.50,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}啦啦啦…  有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:19.54,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}啦啦啦…  還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:24.55,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}啦啦啦…  我和大家的歌
